     * @allow (update) User with auth UID 'user_abc' can update their debt document at /users/user_abc/debts/debt_123.
     * @deny (update) User with auth UID 'user_xyz' cannot update the debt document at /users/user_abc/debts/debt_123.
     * @allow (delete) User with auth UID 'user_abc' can delete their debt document at /users/user_abc/debts/debt_123.
     * @deny (delete) User with auth UID 'user_xyz' cannot delete the debt document at /users/user_abc/debts/debt_123.
     * @principle Enforces document ownership for writes.
