    /**
     * @description Enforces access control for chat history documents under a user's profile.
     *              Only the user with the matching user ID can read and write their own chat history.
     * @path /users/{userId}/chatHistory/{messageId}
     * @allow (create) User with auth UID 'user_abc' can create a new chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @deny (create) User with auth UID 'user_xyz' cannot create a chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @allow (get) User with auth UID 'user_abc' can read their chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @deny (get) User with auth UID 'user_xyz' cannot read the chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @allow (update) User with auth UID 'user_abc' can update their chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @deny (update) User with auth UID 'user_xyz' cannot update the chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @allow (delete) User with auth UID 'user_abc' can delete their chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @deny (delete) User with auth UID 'user_xyz' cannot delete the chat message document at /users/user_abc/chatHistory/message_123.
     * @principle Enforces document ownership for writes.
